==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unowned
<hw>Un*own"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>un-</ets> not + (sense 1) <ets>owned</ets> possessed, and (sense 2)
<ets>owned</ets> granted, acknowledged.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Not owned; having no owner.</def>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not acknowledged; not avowed.</def>
<rj><au>Gay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpack</ent>⟦br⟧
